                                "line": {
                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/pyro/2_savage1_040_012",
                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/pyro/2_savage1_040_022",
                                    "text": "%Pyro%: Obviously you ain't part of the Brotherhood. If anyone in our little group needs watchin' it's her. Mystique's a great one for switchin' sides. But anyway, she's been gone a long time. I was thinkin' someone oughta go into the jungle canal and track her down.",
                                    "textb": "%Pyro%: Hey, I consider it being prudent. Ya can never tell what Mystique's planning next. So I was thinkin' since she's been gone so long that maybe someone should search the jungle canal and track her down.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "text": "%PLAYER%: Do you think Mystique might be hurt?",
                                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: Pyro, are you worried about Mystique?",
                                            "response": {
                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                "line": {
                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/pyro/2_savage1_040_014",
                                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/pyro/2_savage1_040_024",
                                                    "text": "%Pyro%: Oh, heck no. I just want to know what she's planning.",
                                                    "textb": "%Pyro%: Of course not. I want to know what she's got up her sleeve.",
                                                    "response": {
                                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
